data.description: Beautiful 4 sided brick home on full finished basement in Gated Community. High ceilings , tons of molding and trey and vaulted ceilings in many rooms. Main level has Open floor plan great for entertaining. Beautiful Owners Suite on main level with spa like bath, double vanity sink separate tub and shower. Large laundry room with utility sink next to master. Elegant entry foyer. Renovated gourmet cooks kitchen with granite countertops, island with seating, and separate light filled breakfast room. Large deck off kitchen for outdoor dining. Formal living room with fireplace, Family room. Half bath on main. Upper level has two large bedrooms and full bath. Totally finished terrace has high in finishes. Rooms include home office/ play room, exercise room or second home office flex space. Media room and lots of storage and workshop area. Large bedroom and full bath . Could be an in-law or teen sweet. Separate entrance and a covered patio. Fenced yard space and sprinkler system. Tons of space! Award winning Brookwood schools. 2 car garage and additional drive way. 3 separate heat and air systems. Minutes from Shopping, restaurants and more.
